  "texts": [
    "This procedure was repeated in full at 321 lags at 25-ms increments from -4000 ms to 4000 ms relative to word onset.",
    "As a control analysis, for each test word, we used the nearest contextual embedding (in terms of cosine distance) from the training set to predict the brain embedding for the test word.",
    "We used a decoding model to classify unseen words from the corresponding brain embeddings.",
    "The neural signals were first averaged per electrode in ten 62.5-ms bins spanning 625 ms for each lag.",
    "Each bin had 32 data points (the neural recording sampling rate was 512 Hz)."
  ],
